title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Feb 11 2022

description:
Will Hillary be the Democrat nominee in 2024? Clay says that, regarding Kamala Harris, "Honestly, Hillary's way more qualified, probably… If Biden isn't running, I think it has to be Hillary." Joe hurls insult at Lester Holt for easy inflation question. Senator Ron Johnson joins C&B to talk about the miserable failure of what he calls the "covid cartel." Viral clip of vegan feminist talking about the misogyny of meat.
